latestPosts.caption:
Our Karigars have been hard at work on a bunch of new collections that are going to launch over the rest of the year. I know it’s been a while since I launched a whole collection but were starting off with “Mariposa” in June

Mariposa is a delicate collection of jewels which plays with butterflies and flowers encompassing what summer is all about. We’ve tried something different this time - Mother of pearl and I’d be lying if I said I haven’t considered doing everything in MOP going ahead. But I wont get too carried away 🦋 💐
🦋

latestPosts.caption:
Here’s a sneak peek into what’s cooking.
The flame from the blow torch is really mirroring Rajasthan’s heat currently.
I’ve been walking the streets of old Jaipur city with my chappals and jhola and the only thing that seems to help is a nice sweet lassi about 5 times a day.

(The Rover, Brass jewellery, mother of pearl, gold plated, brass jewellery)
